title: Howard Baer - Celtic Mystique
description:
This is the full "Celtic Mystique" album by the composer Howard Baer, my ex-gf and I used to listen to it to put us to sleep, I wasnt able to find it for the longest time. then only recently I found it on a russian video streaming site so I ripped it from the streaming videos... track by track. 

Mp3 format.

Track Listing:

	1	Skibbereen			
	2	Cliffs Of Doneen			
	3	Planxty Lady Wrixon			
	4	Lamentation of Owen Roe O'Neill			
	5	Planxty George Brabazon			
	6	Foggy Dew			
	7	Banks of Cloudy			
	8	Angel of Monmouth

	12	Faire Mehli

You're welcome Amboner.
